OL,7,FThree teenage friends were killed when
OL,8,Fthe car they were travelling in split
OL,9,Fin half following a high-speed
OL,10,Fcollision with a bus.
OL,12,FAn inquest heard that 18-year-old
OL,13,FJesse Owen - who was over the drink
OL,14,Fdrive limit and behind the wheel at
OL,15,Fthe time - along with Morgan Smith,
OL,16,Faged 18, and Callum Griffiths, aged
OL,17,F19, all died when they were thrown
OL,18,Ffrom the Audi A1 car.
