OL,7,FThree others in the car survived the
OL,8,Fcrash in Coedely in Rhondda Cynon Taf,
OL,9,Fwhich happened shortly after the group
OL,10,Fhad attended a funeral.
OL,12,FThe inquest at Pontypridd Coroner's
OL,13,FCourt held on 25 October heard that
OL,14,Fthe car lost control around a bend and
OL,15,Fsplit in two after it collided with a
OL,16,Fbus at Elwyn Street, Coedely,
OL,17,FTonyrefail, on the evening of December
OL,18,F11, 2023.
