OL,7,FOf the six passengers in the car,
OL,8,Fthree died and two suffered serious
OL,9,Finjuries. Survivor Ellis Williams, who
OL,10,Fwas in the front passenger seat at the
OL,11,Ftime of the crash, escaped the vehicle
OL,12,Fwith fewer injuries than Lucas Vaughan
OL,13,Fand Sam Griffiths who were taken to
OL,14,FUniversity Hospital of Wales in
OL,15,FCardiff with life-threatening injuries
OL,16,Fbut survived.
