OL,7,FPost-mortem examinations carried out
OL,8,Fby Dr Stephen Leadbeatter advised Mr
OL,9,FOwen suffered a blunt force injury to
OL,10,Fthe head and chest, Mr Griffiths
OL,11,Flikely died from a blunt head injury,
OL,12,Fand Mr Smith died as a result of
OL,13,Ffractures to his face and neck.
