OL,7,FA toxicology report was carried out by
OL,8,FDr Lawson at University Hospital
OL,9,FBirmingham for Mr Owen. Dr Lawson said
OL,10,Fin Mr Owen's blood he discovered the
OL,11,Fpresence of ethanol (alcohol) at 113mg
OL,12,Fper decilitre in blood, indicating
OL,13,Fconsumption of alcohol prior to death
OL,14,Foccurring. The drink drive limit is
OL,15,F80mg per decilitre.
