OL,7,FThe inquest heard from multiple
OL,8,Fofficers from South Wales Police's
OL,9,Fforensic collision investigation unit
OL,10,Fwho concluded it was likely the
OL,11,Fvehicle had been travelling at between
OL,12,F50 and 55mph on the 20mph road when it
OL,13,Fhit the bus which was "stationary or
OL,14,Falmost stationary".
OL,16,FThe officers told coroner Graeme
OL,17,FHughes conditions on the night were
OL,18,Fdry and the road was damp, adding it
OL,19,Fwas unlikely the teens' deaths were
OL,20,Fcontributed to by the condition of the
OL,21,Froad.
