OL,7,FA number of witnesses who were at the
OL,8,Froadside and saw the Audi vehicle
OL,9,Ftravel past them told the inquest they
OL,10,Ffelt the car was travelling too fast.
OL,12,FMartin Russell, who was running with
OL,13,Fhis running club when he saw the Audi
OL,14,Fgo down the road, said he was shocked
OL,15,Fby how fast the car was travelling.
OL,16,F"The vehicle stood out as I don't
OL,17,Fthink I've ever seen anyone drive that
OL,18,Ffast on that road," he said. He said
OL,19,Fhe asked other members of the running
OL,20,Fclub whether they'd also noticed how
OL,21,Ffast the car was travelling.
