OL,7,FHuw John said he was out walking his
OL,8,Fdog and was talking to his friend
OL,9,Foutside Coedely social club when his
OL,10,Ffriend said: "Look at the f******
OL,11,Fspeed this car is travelling at". "The
OL,12,Fcar flew past us," Mr John said. "Even
OL,13,Fthough it was a small car you could
OL,14,Fhear the engine. I remember thinking:
OL,15,F'Jesus Christ that car was driving too
OL,16,Ffast'."
