OL,7,FPassenger Mr Williams recalled the
OL,8,Fharrowing events on the night of
OL,9,FDecember 11, saying he heard gasps of
OL,10,F"woah" as the vehicle lost control
OL,11,Faround a bend before colliding with
OL,12,Fthe bus. Mr Williams said he was
OL,13,Fsitting in the front passenger seat
OL,14,Fand he recalled the other four sitting
OL,15,Fin the back of the vehicle. He said
OL,16,Fthe vehicle was too small for them all
OL,17,Fto be properly seated and the four in
OL,18,Fthe back must have been on top of each
OL,19,Fother.
