OL,7,F"Jesse drove past the primary school
OL,8,Fand past the Coedely pub," Mr Williams
OL,9,Fsaid. "I thought he was going fast but
OL,10,FI didn't worry." But further into the
OL,11,Fjourney he recalled: "I heard Sam say
OL,12,F'woah' before the bend. I looked to my
OL,13,Fright and I could see Jesse looked
OL,14,Fscared." Mr Williams was the only
OL,15,Fperson who was in the vehicle at the
OL,16,Ftime who was able to provide evidence
OL,17,Fto the inquest.
