OL,7,FThe court heard it wasn't possible to
OL,8,Fdetermine whether Mr Owen had been
OL,9,Fwearing his seatbelt, while evidence
OL,10,Findicated seat belts had not been worn
OL,11,Fin the rear of the vehicle. Two seat
OL,12,Fbelts were fitted to the rear of the
OL,13,Fvehicle because the Audi was designed
OL,14,Ffor maximum occupancy of four people,
OL,15,Fmeaning it is likely at least two
OL,16,Fpeople in the rear of the car at the
OL,17,Ftime were not wearing seat belts.
