OL,7,FPC Evans, who visited the scene after
OL,8,Fthe crash, noted seat belts in the
OL,9,Frear of the vehicle appeared in
OL,10,Fserviceable condition with no
OL,11,Fcollision damage.
OL,13,FCoroner Mr Hughes was told that would
OL,14,Fsuggest that the two passengers that
OL,15,Fwere perhaps sitting on the seats
OL,16,Fthemselves in the rear of the vehicle
OL,17,Fwere also not wearing seat belts or
OL,18,Fdidn't have their seat belts in the
OL,19,F"extended position".
